
= Bibwiki release notes =

== Recent changes ==

= 0.99e =

= 0.99d =

*    12.2007 - a lot of code rewriting, bug fixing etc.
* 02.12.2007 - integrate OSBiB
* 02.12.2007 - integrate Cite.php
* 02.12.2007 - compact view of bibliography

= 0.99c =

* 05.11.2007 - fixed: search string for ISBN links in scheme "AT Vienna -- UB"
* 05.11.2007 - new library scheme "US Washington -- LoC"
* 05.11.2007 - moved tab links to sidebar "bibwiki toolbox" 
* 05.11.2007 - fixed: $wgDefaultBib opened if nothing else specified
* 05.11.2007 - fixed: check if $wgTitleLinkTags is empty
* 05.11.2007 - fixed: check if $wgISBNLinkTags is empty
* 20.10.2007 - added LoC import feature
* 19.10.2007 - per-user bibliographies
* 19.10.2007 - added bibliography dropdown box in record creation page
* 14.10.2007 - fixed some minor bugs
* 14.10.2007 - added ArXiv library settings
* 14.10.2007 - added ArXiv import feature
* 12.10.2007 - "arxiv" tags are linked to ArXiv
* 10.10.2007 - fixed wfRenderBibliographyTitle
* 10.10.2007 - Bibwiki can deal with empty file now
* 07.10.2007 - integrated Mediawiki's group management in Bibwiki
* 07.10.2007 - "file", "pdf" are aliases for "docname"
* 07.10.2007 - using Mediawikis internationalisation
* 07.10.2007 - updated for Mediawiki 1.11
* 07.10.2007 - new class Bibliography

= 0.99b =

* 09.06.2007 - fixed bottom navbar error
* 08.06.2007 - fixed user CSS 
* 08.06.2007 - fixed key non-uniqueness bug
* 07.06.2007 - fixed docname delimiters
* 07.06.2007 - fixed <Title>-translation in saveUrl()
* 30.05.2007 - added settings checks
* 18.05.2007 - added language settings
* 18.05.2007 - added library settings
* 17.05.2007 - fixed special char keyword conversion in opac import
* 17.05.2007 - added $wgTitleLinkTags
* 25.04.2007 - automatic delimiter conversion
* 19.04.2007 - $wgConvertSpecialCharsToTeXCommands implemented
* 15.04.2007 - action "save_settings" implemented
* 14.04.2007 - action "load_settings" implemented
* 14.04.2007 - warning message appears if default password is used
* 09.04.2007 - apdated Special:Search, searches through all .bib-files in 
               $wgBibPath
* 06.04.2007 - added "export from document" feature
* 06.04.2007 - current Bibfile is also stored in cookie "BIBWIKI_BIBFILE"
* 06.04.2007 - diacritics in docname will be translated to normal ASCII
               characters
* 01.01.2007 - doi numbers are now linked
* 01.01.2007 - sanity checks in export() added
* 01.01.2007 - fixed spacing in viewStatistics()
* 01.01.2007 - export() reports BibTeX errors
* 01.01.2007 - fixed export(): missing hidden field "action=export" inserted
* 01.01.2007 - fixed wpl.bst and sws.bst
* 01.01.2007 - bbl2html.pl rewritten to PHP code and integrated in Bibwiki.php
* 01.01.2007 - fixed removeOldBackups()
* 01.01.2007 - fixed filter splitting
* 01.01.2007 - re-fixed convertPublisher()
* 01.01.2007 - fixed UTF8 conversation in URL import
* 01.01.2007 - fixed getBibfileName()
* 01.01.2007 - Bibwiki can now deal with @Book(...) entries
* 01.01.2007 - added $wgValueDelim... and $wgTitleDelim... to define Delimiters
* 01.01.2007 - fixed URL import
* 01.01.2007 - fixed getBibfileName
* 01.01.2007 - encapsulated access functions to bibfile, which leads to slimmer
               view...() functions and reduces bugs.
* 01.01.2007 - completed redesign to a MediaWiki extension.